{
  "stem": "11957.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They shot back at us, and we had a battle on our hands.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's what it us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so you-- I mean, you were involved in basically trying to eliminate them and shooting them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hm, that's right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not hand-to-hand, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I lost quite a-- a number of-- of good people there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About 200 miles.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we had wagons and horses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Horses and wagons-- we moved around with horses and wagons.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we didn't hear anything on the camps.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you were basically kind of cut off from the outside world.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we were cut off from the outside world.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we heard some stories.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they were coming with trucks and loading up the-- the peoples that  were in ghetto, taking them out to the airport, where they were digging-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ditches.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they-- they dug out ditches, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 10 feet deep and 20 feet wide and 30 feet long.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when-- when we still were in the ghetto, we inquired about these ditches.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they said they were going to store potatoes in them for the winter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's what they told us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the meantime, they used it to shoot people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They used it to shoot the population in there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At least one a week.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At least one a week.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to do some reconnaissance and find out at what times they're going by a certain area.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was pretty good at it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I usually used to go and get the reconnaissance, how many trains go by a certain area where it was beneficial for us to-- to blow up that area.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Local population.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we didn't have any infiltrators.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
